Â Â Â deploy.py --build --branch $(Build.SourceBranchName)
creates inqu-worker image depending on branch.

Â Â dev: inqu-worker:v0.0.54-dev
Â Â Â release/0.1.0:inqu-worker:v0.1.3-release/0.1.0
Â Â main: inqu-worker:v1.1.0
Â Â feature: inqu-worker:v.0.0.55-feature12345
Â Â hotfix: inqu-worker:v.0.1.3-hotfix12345
Â e) clean upÂ Â
3) Flux Image Reflector Controller find new tag.
